%h1.title Number Puzzle

%div.board
  %div.row
    %div.tile#tile-1 1
    %div.tile#tile-2 2
    %div.tile#tile-3 3
    %div.tile#tile-4 4
  %div.row
    %div.tile#tile-5 5
    %div.tile#tile-6 6
    %div.tile#tile-7 7
    %div.tile#tile-8 8
  %div.row
    %div.tile#tile-9 9
    %div.tile#tile-10 10
    %div.tile#tile-11 11
    %div.tile#tile-12 12
  %div.row
    %div.tile#tile-13 13
    %div.tile#tile-14 14
    %div.tile#tile-15 15
    %div.tile#tile-blank &nbsp;
  %div.controls
    %a.btn#hint-button Hint
    %a.btn#shuffle-button Shuffle
    %a.btn#count-button Count
    %a.btn#solve-button Solve

%div.game-over
  %h3.title.solved Solved!
  %p
    %strong Steps:
    %span#steps 0
    %br
    %strong Target Steps:
    %span#optimal 0
    %br
    %strong Hints:
    %span#hints 0

%div.instructions
  %h3.title Instructions
  %p
    Keyboard based
    %a{ href: 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/15_puzzle' }
      15-puzzle
    \.
  %ul
    %li Shuffle the board by clicking the "Shuffle" button or with the spacebar
    %li To move the blue tile use arrows or slide if you are playing with your mobile.
    %li Get a hint of the next ideal move by pressing the button or "q" in your keyboard
    %li Check how you did with the "Count" button or by pressing the "n" key.
    %li Give up? Solve the puzzle with the "Solve" button or the "s" key.
